$ /usr/lib/cups

`/usr/lib/cups` is the default → Linux/CUPS[CUPS] *ServerBin* directory for → Linux/CUPS[CUPS]. It contains the following directories
  • backend
  • cgi-bin
  • daemon
  • driver
  • → Linux/fhs/usr/lib/cups/filter[filter]
  • monitor
  • notifier

To put the directory to another location, the `ServerBin` directive must be used in → Linux/fhs/etc/cups/cups-files_conf.
